title: The Chase viewers in meltdown as only ONE contestant gets through to the final round with £100k in the bank - but does she scoop the jackpot?
text:
Mrs Crunch 'one of the tensest final chases ever' The Chase viewers in meltdown as only ONE contestant gets through to the final round with £100k in the bank – but does she scoop the jackpot? 
Andrea has been heralded for her bravery - despite giving the SAME wrong answer as the Dark Destroyer, in an attempt to push him back Video
